WEBVTT

00:00:01.272 --> 00:00:02.649
Predstavljajte si tole:

00:00:02.649 --> 00:00:03.742
ponedeljek zjutraj je,

00:00:03.742 --> 00:00:04.861
v službi ste,

00:00:04.861 --> 00:00:06.615
vstopate v delovni dan

00:00:06.615 --> 00:00:09.437
in potem sodelavec, ki ga bežno poznate,

00:00:09.437 --> 00:00:11.273
stopi k vaši pisalni mizi

00:00:11.273 --> 00:00:12.675
in vam ukrade stol.

00:00:12.675 --> 00:00:13.917
Nič ne reče,

00:00:13.917 --> 00:00:15.305
samo odpelje ga.

00:00:15.305 --> 00:00:17.788
Ne pove vam, zakaj je vzel vaš stol

00:00:17.788 --> 00:00:19.849
namesto katerega drugega.

00:00:19.849 --> 00:00:22.041
Ne vzame v zakup,
da vi stol morda potrebujete,

00:00:22.041 --> 00:00:23.582
da bi lahko opravili svoje delo.

00:00:23.582 --> 00:00:25.839
Tega si ne dovolite. 
Ukrepali boste.

00:00:25.839 --> 00:00:27.866
Sledili boste temu tipu

00:00:27.866 --> 00:00:31.178
in vprašali: "Zakaj moj stol?"